>\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"見到白衫黑社會拿住棍你又唔拉？"},{"pid":"b52d81123f9caea22ffe4e657785ae7a66d68a0c","tid":1384510,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5日大罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"615ac8ed7dd16232a84be1e8e0a0611cbbb1a254","tid":1384510,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd48fa2c8b51ac6a510d8a6356a5b5abd148dae1","tid":1384510,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"香港警察 吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c62111fd88b547daa3b376f629ec206e0865a2","tid":1384510,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"有用 推"},{"pid":"d48bc499b813a061b59e9fe3ef8d2f65e1e0b139","tid":1384510,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"全民8月5曰大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"7cab45cfd040e204ff625ad4803487557fa7f441","tid":1384510,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198ea42d8a612b47457aa319ab9d0f2472f3db08","tid":1384510,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c708f12800d32ec21d9a77ee8b0ed862d7beec","tid":1384510,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9dbdc6993ac5ed7365e88b5a7c48a50ab41d244","tid":1384510,"uid":188256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"8aaafc75da6ee51be7e9c2fe01ddac6b70118e42","tid":1384510,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy